    dc:description "Figure 11. Xylopia rubescens. A Habit with fruit B Inner petal, adaxial surface C Outer petal, adaxial surface D, E Stamens, abaxial view F Staminode, abaxial view G Stigma apex H Inflorescence I Seed, longitudinal view. A from Brenan et al. 8022 (K), B-H from Angus 870 (MO) I from Breteler et al. 10446 (WAG, spirit collection)." ;
